
libdbi-drivers - drivers for libdbi, the Database
Independent Abstraction Layer for C

Copyright (C) 2001-2002, Markus Hoenicka <markus at mhoenicka.de>
http://libdbi-drivers.sourceforge.net


POSTGRESQL DRIVER:
------------------

This driver allows libdbi-enabled applications to use PostgreSQL as a database
backend. Internally, it provides a libdbi driver around the libpq client
library.

See the included driver documentation for installation instructions, usage,
and information about driver-specific peculiarities.


